{"tid":2027318,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四工會遭拒見 八傳媒組織促PK鄧 嚴懲違規惡警","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T11:09:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d09478d085c313ff47ed68910194ad42cf46cd6e","tid":2027318,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:59:55.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/XQHDEOAXMKFWRDH46ZPCTBXCHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FXQHDEOAXMKFWRDH46ZPCTBXCHQ%2F&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV0qdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=6a74a26a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FXQHDEOAXMKFWRDH46ZPCTBXCHQ%2F&h=03d5a52a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200521/XQHDEOAXMKFWRDH46ZPCTBXCHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n四工會遭拒見<br />\n八傳媒組織促PK鄧 嚴懲違規惡警<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【黑色母親節】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處長鄧炳強口口聲聲指警方暴力對待記者不理想，又揚言會檢討，惟前線記者採訪時被警員毆打噴椒的情況繼續無日無之。5.10母親節當晚大批記者在旺角採訪反修例活動時，警員包圍截查，無理要求蹲下、錄影個人資料，更粗暴地近距離狂噴胡椒噴劑、箍頸近20秒、以圓盾𠝹傷記者手臂致大面積脫皮。鄧炳強今日與四個傳媒組織代表會面，聲稱冀與新聞界加強溝通，卻將四間傳媒工會拒諸門外，被質疑只是做公關騷。八個組織要求鄧炳強嚴懲5.10違規警員。<br />\n<br />\n記者：謝明明 廖承志<br />\n<br />\n警方5.10當晚暴力對待前線記者，八個傳媒工會及組織早前聯署抗議，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n香港攝影記者協會、獨立評論人協會及大專新聞教育工作者聯席，卻拒見四間傳媒工會，包括壹傳媒工會、明報職工協會、香港電台節目製作人員工會及眾新聞工會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995087_fd68.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995087_fd68.gif&h=93d6c9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批記者本月10日在旺角通菜街採訪期間，防暴警突然包抄並向記者施放胡椒噴劑。明報職工協會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995085_29e3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995085_29e3.gif&h=61b2be48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《明報》攝記5.10在西洋菜南街被速龍小隊用盾牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995085_e1f1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995085_e1f1.gif&h=58480da3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年11.17眾新聞記者在理大疑遭閃光彈擊中右腿。眾新聞工會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995086_45c9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995086_45c9.gif&h=cc2b9d09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本報記者去年10.1在尖沙嘴及佐敦一帶疑中彈受傷。壹傳媒工會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥選擇性會面做騷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：遇襲《蘋果》攝記擬聯同行家索償<br />\n<br />\n四間傳媒工會昨向鄧炳強發出聯署公開信，對警方拒見表示極度憤怒及遺憾，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，<br />\n更遭警員以頭壓向頭部；《壹週刊》記者採訪助理警務處長陶輝涉嫌僭建一事時，遭警方以遊蕩罪拘捕及擅取採訪簿等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995086_665c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995086_665c.gif&h=bade4839&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾新聞記者5月10日在旺角採訪期間，警察揮棍驅散在場記者。眾新聞工會提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200521/large/1589995087_c663.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589995087_c663.gif&h=020a2fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求向受傷記者道歉<br />\n<br />\n信件指出，曾有傳媒被警方拍攝記者證後，相片遭廣泛流傳。5.10當晚警方要求記者對着鏡頭說出個人資料，更令人擔心片段會流出。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n今日與鄧炳強會面的傳媒組織聯同四間傳媒工會發聲明，強烈要求鄧炳強嚴肅整治警隊，立即停止對傳媒的語言或肢體暴力；<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n「假記者」及「假記者證」指控及交出具體改善方案。<br />\n<br />\n近日有人鼓吹「官方記者認證制度」，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n等同親手扼殺香港的新聞自由。"},{"pid":"0fa8a5d745110ee866f6fd09df17f9be77922590","tid":2027318,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"曱甴王鄧炳強連show都唔做<br />\n反正就快23條<br />\n拉晒你d人返去都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a0da692e5db93e427775317d2b5d88ce048149","tid":2027318,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"直接23條將蘋果立場獨媒hkfp等等網媒全部危害國家安全落閘封鋪<br />\n洗驚你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}